    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<br><br>在这个2.5D动作冒险平台中，使用您的火焰来战胜潜伏在被毁哥特式城堡阴影中的威胁生物，利用动态难度系统，穿越具有挑战性的平台部分，解决神奇的超现实绘画中的神秘谜题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879680/extras/6e24b036230f4b4688c78e952b0d815b.poster.avif?t=1747706066\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879680/extras/6e24b036230f4b4688c78e952b0d815b.webm?t=1747706066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879680/extras/6e24b036230f4b4688c78e952b0d815b.mp4?t=1747706066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>用你的火对抗黑暗</strong></h2>使用火焰与在每个角落等待着你的神秘敌人战斗，通过学习新的能力，让你的光芒更加明亮，因为你勇敢地击退黑暗，并在战斗中使用它们来帮助你，或者在城堡的大厅中发现新的秘密。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一个动态的游戏难度系统</strong></h2>根据你的优势使用ignis自适应难度系统，可以更快地移动并对你的敌人造成更大的伤害，但要小心，因为他们也会变得更危险。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879680/extras/fd99b00459859a2a8e8b2f08dc960955.poster.avif?t=1747706066\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879680/extras/fd99b00459859a2a8e8b2f08dc960955.webm?t=1747706066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879680/extras/fd99b00459859a2a8e8b2f08dc960955.mp4?t=1747706066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>解开超现实绘画中的谜团</strong></h2>进入神秘的绘画，进入一个超现实的、未探索的奇迹世界，并发现藏在画布里的秘密。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>2.5D平台化作用</strong></h2>充满陷阱和敌人的挑战性平台部分。穿过迷人的图书馆、令人惊叹的阳台和城堡危险的军械库。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879680/extras/97f8990c2228e23dd689bada9601f732.poster.avif?t=1747706066\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879680/extras/97f8990c2228e23dd689bada9601f732.webm?t=1747706066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879680/extras/97f8990c2228e23dd689bada9601f732.mp4?t=1747706066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>惊人的视觉效果和人物</strong></h2>探索城堡各种环境中令人惊叹的景色，并发现遍布城堡的独特人物，以了解您周围超现实世界的奥秘。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>把光带回来</strong></h2>在这个超现实、哥特式的世界里，扮演一个迷人的烛台，试图恢复家中的光线，这是一座废弃的城堡。<br><br><br>你的火焰代表希望，还是只会带来毁灭？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879680/extras/c50df8740cd6d0056ee2e53971972a88.poster.avif?t=1747706066\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879680/extras/c50df8740cd6d0056ee2e53971972a88.webm?t=1747706066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879680/extras/c50df8740cd6d0056ee2e53971972a88.mp4?t=1747706066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
